ANIMATION_COMPLETE

Motion Personality Statement:
Wings moves like a machine being configured — precise, inevitable, physical.
Every transition answers a question: what just changed, what does it mean,
how powerful is this thing. Nothing decorates. Everything informs.

Files Built:

1. src/components/ui/CountUp.tsx
   - Reusable animated number count-up using useMotionValue + animate
   - Auto-duration based on value magnitude (small numbers finish fast)
   - prefers-reduced-motion: instant final value

2. src/lib/sound.ts
   - Procedural paper/stamp sound via AudioContext (no audio file)
   - 80ms decaying white noise burst, gain 0.3
   - Off by default — user opt-in via localStorage wings_sound_enabled

3. src/components/features/catalog/VariantCeremony.tsx
   - Context + Provider + hook for the Variant Selection Ceremony
   - ceremonyKey changes on each variant selection — all subscribed components re-animate
   - Tracks previousSpecs and currentSpecs for delta-aware transitions
   - Integration instructions in file header comment

4. src/components/features/catalog/SpecScannerLine.tsx
   - Gold scan line (1px, opacity 0.6) sweeps down spec table on scroll entry
   - rAF-based animation: rowCount * 20ms total duration
   - Absolute positioned, pointer-events none, fades out after scan
   - prefers-reduced-motion: skip, lines just appear

5. src/components/features/catalog/MagneticButton.tsx
   - Magnetic cursor pull within configurable radius (default 60px)
   - useSpring { stiffness: 200, damping: 20 } for smooth return to center
   - Touch/coarse pointer: no effect (SSR-safe)
   - Document-level mousemove listener for pull that starts before cursor is over button

6. src/components/features/catalog/ProductHpMeter.tsx (modified)
   - Dot overshoots target by 5% then settles: spring { stiffness: 300, damping: 18, mass: 1 }
   - Bar fill delayed 80ms behind dot — the two land separately, reinforcing physicality
   - Ambient pulse: scale [1, 1.002, 1] on 4s infinite loop — the machine breathes
   - CountUp component for the HP number (count-up on viewport entry)
   - prefers-reduced-motion: all animations disabled, CountUp instant

Ceremony Integration Pending:
  ProductSpecTable.tsx — integration agent to wire VariantCeremonyProvider
  and per-cell AnimatePresence exit-up/enter-below with ceremonyKey as key prop.
